name: Obsidev
body:
# A French software company
Obsidev is a software company which is developing different kind of (mostly open-source) software.
To know more, you can visit the [Obsidev website](http://www.obsidev.com)

## GuiPro
See the [GuiPro project page](/guipro/)

## Aurora Game Engine
A game engine developed by Jean-Matthieu COULON and Jerome GLATIGNY for [Aurora Studio](http://www.aurora-studio.com/)
Even if the project is down and Aurora Studio has moved to Unity ; we wanted to release the source code and we hope to be able to re-work on the project one day.
https://github.com/obsidev/aurora-game-engine
